snippet.title: TRIANGLE STRATEGY - Character & Story Trailer #3: Benedict Pascal - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Learn about Benedict, Steward of House Wolffort, and the choices and characters you'll be faced with in the third character and story trailer for TRIANGLE STRATEGY. Test the weight of your convictions in this upcoming turn-based strategy RPG from Square Enix. The decisions you make determines who joins you, will impact the path the story takes and ultimately, its outcome. Who will rise and who will fall? 

Available 3/4/22: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/triangle-strategy-switch/
